These are the STL and SVG designs for the Chiron bed that can be used in PRUSA Slicer.

Copy these files to someplace on your HD.
In PRUSA Slcier select the Chiron Profile you want to add the bed to.
Select Printer Settings --> General --> Bed Shape and the SET button

The Texture will be the SVG file, Model will be the STL file.

Note the bed is not transparent so you can't look up from the underneath
the bed in PRUSA Slicer.
